  "question": "What features would you expect to find in a patient with haemor-rhagic shock? A Decrease in catecholamine secretion B Oxygen–haemoglobin dissocia-tion curve shifted to the right C Stimulation of aortic chemoreceptors D Increase in tidal ventilation E Decrease in antidiuretic hormone (ADH) secretion",
