  "question": "A 9-year-old boy was referred to orthopaedic outpatients with a 6-week history of left leg pain. X-rays revealed a large mass in the femur. Bone biopsy is per-formed and reveals small round blue cells. Which of the follow-ing is the most likely diagnosis?",
