  "question": "A 36-year-old man has a neck tumour. It has damaged his left cervical sympathetic chain\nganglion. Which of the following physical signs would you expect? A Increased sweat secretion on the\nleft side of the face\nB Lateral deviation of the left eye\nC Pale skin on the left side of his face\nD Ptosis on the left\nE Pupil dilatation of the left eye",
