  "question": "Which one of the following changes in disease patterns has occurred in Europe and North America over the past 50 years? A The death rate from lung cancer in females has fallen B The death rate from lung cancer in males has risen in recent years C The numbers infected with the HIV virus has fallen D The death rate from suicide has fallen E The death rate from gastric carci-noma has fallen",
