  "question": "The virus responsible for caus-ing acquired immunodeficiency syndrome (AIDS) has which one of the following features?\nA A double-stranded genome\nB Lacks a viral envelope\nC Lacks reverse transcriptase\nD Is a member of the adenovirus group\nE Destroys CD4 T-lymphocytes",
